{"tid":898032,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邊一個發明了英文","createTime":"2018-11-11T11:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T15:25:22.000Z","uid":156130,"like":14,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8bda8daad9932db5b72713833eb706849c34e9c9","tid":898032,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"其實我想知發明英文條友用咩原理做字<br />\n<br />\nbook<br />\ncook<br />\nlook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個字頭一唔同就成個字意思唔同<br />\n中文都話有象形形聲會意指事......<br />\n英文感覺好似見到樣嘢抽籤咁抽幾個字母拼出嚟話呢個字就呢個意思咁~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nyesterday I go to school by bus<br />\n加個yesterday就已經只係過咗去啦，又要發明過去式，加ed就算啦，又要有d冇原因咁成個轉，仲要轉到連字頭都唔同埋<br />\n發明時態條友應該好得閒"},{"pid":"e20cb7e11136df2ddcfcaaaaa859d933f0a3b0b1","tid":898032,"uid":192491,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"你覺得發明語言係得一條友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b63beaa83f859f6c095a5305de88ffc10d84349","tid":898032,"uid":109655,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:58:37.000Z","msg":"中文字個部首唔同左都意思會唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd000b45a5d4028f73e88a2bb67ac44646ee036","tid":898032,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"語感問題"},{"pid":"e2a28c603d7e20367688ad6cccc9e5399e11ac1c","tid":898032,"uid":208722,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"你覺得全世界得英文有咁嘅文法？<br />\n<br />\n喺歐陸嚟講已經數一數二簡單&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e87e91ac41bee0636f0cbb8eb5c2ecfdbb180c33","tid":898032,"uid":108502,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"建議樓主去搵吓Piraha<br />\n隻語言應該幾岩你用<br />\n冇顏色 冇數字 冇任何未來過去時態<br />\n淨係得現在式<br />\n發音又少"},{"pid":"da44cb9cd31abdcbe0612d9ae8a9d77b70eb2396","tid":898032,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b63beaa83f859f6c095a5305de88ffc10d84349","tid":898032,"u